response.overview: Gather everyone around the TV with some popcorn to watch Dora the Explorer: Dora Rocks. It's time to sing, dance and explore in three exciting adventures. This Dora Rocks DVD tells the story of how Benny forgets to send his party invitations. The main character and Boots need your help bringing their microphone to his barn so they can call their friends to join them at the fiesta. Cross the Noisy River and other obstacles, and then join the starlet in her special pop-star outfit to perform a special song with all her friends at the sing-along. Then, keep going in two more musical adventures in Nickelodeon Dora Rocks. It makes a thoughtful gift idea for a birthday, holiday or any other occasion.
response.title: Dora the Explorer: Dora Rocks!
